{"tid":247282,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實智商有無得遺傳？","createTime":"2017-05-17T16:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T03:23:34.000Z","uid":64800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1f32707ce96a9e5407b25a07d0e44e760b9a654","tid":247282,"uid":64800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:08:42.000Z","msg":"例如好似鋼練咁<br />\n愛德華係天才練金術師<br />\n佢老豆又真係ok勁既 睇落似有遺傳<br />\n<br />\n再睇返現實 就好似其他大學教授or大學生家庭啲仔女都好似讀書醒啲<br />\n<br />\n我知家庭環境都係主要原因、但係係咪真係咁關事呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再假設將果啲高學歷家庭既小朋友由細放落個普通家庭成長會點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但如果智商真係會遺傳既話，啲天才既仔女點解好似一個二個都無乜成就（可能有我唔知掛）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297481bd7cf714278a2bebbb087bc98acc89639d","tid":247282,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:14:38.000Z","msg":"個人經驗：突變居多<br />\n<br />\n我一家三兄弟，兩老、二哥都唔係醒目人，唯獨我大佬轉數快到痴線、過目不忘、應對能力強、港大GPA3.7Grade Grade。<br />\n<br />\n自己就濕尻U都讀到想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e53fded251903361aa7e2bb92d589c26f8b266","tid":247282,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:15:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個人經驗：突變居多<br />\n<br />\n我一家三兄弟，兩老、二哥都唔係醒目人，唯獨我大佬轉數快到痴線、過目不忘、應對能力強、港大GPA3.7 Grade。<br />\n<br />\n自己就濕尻U都讀到想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0c357afad37bffb779f99e3ef47ecc3e56d58481","tid":247282,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:25:00.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n查下陶哲軒全家就知"},{"pid":"f3fa2711b83fde08463220e6c897d2faee28b1dd","tid":247282,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T